Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:07.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1122,660)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.17,0:01:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我全年最爱的时节就是水母大迁徙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the jellyfish migration is my favorite time of year
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整整三天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For three whole days
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.08,0:01:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界的水母都会聚到一处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,jellyfish from around the globe gather on one spot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.20,0:01:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分享水母的小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to trade jelly secrets
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, look
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝冠爆爆水母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A blue-crested blaster
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.64,0:01:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没见过这种水母  太稀有了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen one before, they're really rare
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.10,0:01:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斑点喷喷水母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:25.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a speckled squirter
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.43,0:01:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双拳跳跳水母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A two-fisted jumper
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,金嗓子刺刺水母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a golden-throated stinger
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今年的大迁徙一定特别盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This year's migration is gonna be a big one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来得出动可靠好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This looks like a job for ol' reliable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(494,668)}可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:10.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1142,370)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天真是最美好的捉水母日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the most beautiful day of jellyfishing ever
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.67,0:02:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的破网一只都没捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't catch a thing with my dumb old net
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我有可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky for me, I have ol' reliable
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碳纤维网柄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carbon-fiber handle
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钛合金网体  人体工学硅胶握把
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,titanium-alloy netting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and form-fitting silicone grips
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可靠好朋友是世上最厉害的网
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ol' reliable is the best net in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.01,0:02:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁可拼了命都要那样的网
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would kill for a net like that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像是拼了萝卜这种小东西了命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somethin' small, like a carrot
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.32,0:02:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛不行  看着难受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not spiders, they're icky
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-night, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好迎接水母大迁徙的第二天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get ready
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for day two of the jellyfish migration
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.10,0:02:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先拿出我可靠的水母网  可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with my trusty jellyfishing net, old reliable
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ol' reliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(888,130)}可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对  裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, pants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,穿了一条裤子后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  可靠好朋友被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, ol' reliable's been stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,916)}可靠好朋友失窃
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往那边贴一张  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put one over there, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贴完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all done
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能应该再传开一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should spread out a little
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928,942)}裤头村报\N可靠好朋友失窃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(376,490)}水母大迁徙
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.84,0:03:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.82,0:03:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精彩的水母大迁徙已经进入第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The jellyfish migration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,enters its second day of fantastic jellyfishing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,490)}第二天
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在连线现场记者了解情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We now go live to our reporter on the scene
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今年的迁徙规模为本世纪最大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This year's migration is the largest in a century
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很同情某些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel truly sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场盛会哪怕错过了一分钟的可怜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the poor saps who will miss
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even one minute of this remarkable event
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请注意  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的水母网被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My jellyfishing net has been stolen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要完好无损归还  将有巨额奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am prepared to offer a large reward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for its safe return
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much we talkin' about?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十二块  还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,$12 and
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.62,0:03:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两块  十块
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two, 10
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.33,0:03:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十块
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,twenty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三毛八
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,38 cents
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on the case
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然今天新闻少  你们也别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys, I know it's a slow news day, but come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  网找回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, did you get your net back?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧挂了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off the line, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能会有谁打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone might be trying to call
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提供可靠好朋友的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about ol' reliable
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,网找回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you get your net yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.82,0:04:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没找到我的网就别打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't call unless you found my net
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.58,0:04:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  找到你的网了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I found your net
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,really, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.66,0:04:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不完全真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not really
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是有点寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just got lonely
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我网再也找不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never get my net back
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.74,0:04:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可靠好朋友彻底丢了  只能认命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that ol' reliable is gone forever
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.58,0:04:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大半夜还能用自己的水母网捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gets to practice in the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with his jellyfishing net
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇怪的是  派大星的网昨天就散架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny thing is, Patrick's net disintegrated yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  可靠好朋友找回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, did you get ol' reliable back yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not yet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  要是你偷了我的水母网
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, wouldn't it be the funniest thing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,岂不是太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you had taken my jellyfish net?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.02,0:05:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  那样就太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that would be silly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想起来了  我要送你个礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, I got you a present
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A present, what is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是坦白熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a confess-a-bear
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把所有秘密告诉这位特别的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a special friend you tell all your secrets to
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先走了  你们两个慢慢聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just leave you two alone to get acquainted
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名字是坦白熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"My name is confess-a-bear"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向我说出你所有秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Tell me all your secrets"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.70,0:05:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最近做了件不那么光彩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did something recently I'm not proud of
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是故意要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正就是发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It just sort of happened
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你应该说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Maybe you should talk about it"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.62,0:05:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那还牵扯到我最好的朋友海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it involves my best friend, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然他好像不知道  但
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think he knows what happened, but
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他发现了  会很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would really upset him if he found out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟坦白熊说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Tell confess-a-bear"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经说太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've said too much, already
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟坦白熊说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Tell confess-a-bear now"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.05,0:06:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Now"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不小心把海绵宝宝的牙刷碰倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I accidentally knocked SpongeBob's toothbrush
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掉进了马桶里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into the toilet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.93,0:06:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我没洗就把它放回台上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then I put it back on the counter without washing it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.61,0:06:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坦白熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Confess-a-bear?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没对我生气吧  坦白熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're mad at me, aren't you, confess-a-bear?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, we need to talk
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't come in
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没穿好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not decent
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.27,0:06:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The house is a mess
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有核泄漏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a radiation leak
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯怎么给关了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are the lights off?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在里面  马上就出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in here, be out in a second
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ol' reliable
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.25,0:06:48.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:48.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你手上是啥  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in your hand, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另一只手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in your other hand?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我另一只手也没拿东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing in my other hand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, bye
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星不会偷可靠好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick wouldn't steal ol' reliable
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would he?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁可拼了命也要那样的网
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would kill for a net like that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道我最好的朋友一直是个江洋大盗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have I been best friends with a master thief?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非弄清楚不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must know for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天要干嘛  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you gonna do today, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我去上班了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off to work, see you later
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.82,0:07:36.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:36.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.79,0:07:44.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要来看看你怎么没干嘛  小毛贼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we'll just see what sort of nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're really up to, Sneaky McSneakypants
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,八小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is good
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想真正了解某个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never really know a guy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.75,0:07:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得用高倍率望远镜盯他个八小时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until you've stared at him for eight hours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through high-powered binoculars
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.60,0:08:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.95,0:08:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothin'
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚干完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just finished
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(284,560)}待办事项单\N没干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, look
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.06,0:08:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里可以看到我刚站的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can see where I was just standin' from here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  你要是有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, if you'd wanted to
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全就能整天在这里监视我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you could have spied on me all day from right here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很怪异吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Creepy, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之你拿着这副望远镜干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what are you doin' with those binoculars?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.97,0:08:25.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没望远镜  看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:25.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have any binoculars, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're acting weird
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没表现很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not acting weird
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现才奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're acting weird
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.12,0:08:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,acting
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.84,0:08:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,weird
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, bye
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, young fellow
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿意花大价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to pay top dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买有着特殊意义的捉水母工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for jellyfishing items with sentimental value
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该懂我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you know what I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小道消息说  你知道要上哪去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Word on the street is that you know where to get
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高质量捉水母工具  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,quality jellyfishing supplies, hmm?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪个道说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What street said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这条道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was it this one?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管好你自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Star
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你手上有个稀有水母网
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know that you are in possession
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of a rare jellyfishing net
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.85,0:09:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿意出十亿买下那张网
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will pay $1 billion for that net
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我绝对不会把这个水母网给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you're not getting this jellyfishing net
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算你出一百万也不卖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't sell it for a million dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百也不卖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not for a $100
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算出一块我也不卖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even sell it for $1
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算出多少都不卖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't have it for any price
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西对我来说比钱重要多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This means more to me than money
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我朋友海绵宝宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my friend SpongeBob's
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.14,0:09:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个可怕的八字胡男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There was a scary guy with a moustache
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在问一大堆怪问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,asking a lot of weird questions
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我就是那个可怕八字胡男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I'm the scary moustache guy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, SpongeBob, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要戴这么可怕的八字胡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would you wear such a scary moustache?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要偷走我的水母网
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you steal my jellyfishing net?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.17,0:09:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你再也不是我最好的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这个偷水母网的坏小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you no-good jellyfishing net thief
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you think that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你亲口说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because you said it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说那是你朋友海绵宝宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it was your friend SpongeBob's
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gift
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.29,0:10:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我要给朋友海绵宝宝的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my friend SpongeBob's gift
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你做了个新网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made you a new net
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,712)}送给海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送给海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"For SpongeBob"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我做了个新水母网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made me a new jellyfishing net?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is so thoughtful of you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.09,0:10:16.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:16.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛  最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you doing, best friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是你最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not your best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.57,0:10:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个偷水母网的坏小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a no-good jelly netting thief fish
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.47,0:10:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁着还有尊严  离开裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving Bikini Bottom while I still have my dignity
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1166,464)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们情谊已尽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, this is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非有什么意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barring the unforeseen hand of fate
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.27,0:10:40.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:40.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid it is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起我冤枉了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I accused you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然丢了网已经够糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough I lost my net
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我也不想丢了我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose my best friend, too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the hold up?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你们俩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好  你又把网落在公交上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, you left your net on the bus again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可靠好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old reliable?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把你落在公交上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I left you on the bus?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你每周都落公交上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do it every week
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还走不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, can we get going?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  请你收下这个当作纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I want you to take this to remember me by
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要把可靠好朋友送给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're giving me old reliable?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我接受你的道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I accept your apology
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  傻大个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here, you big lug
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.18,0:11:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们次次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They do this all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm serious
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要留在裤头村不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm staying in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去捉水母吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wanna go jellyfishing?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚有了个新网
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just got a new net
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So did I
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我最好的朋友给我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My best friend made it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.60,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&\fsp50}木偶章鱼哥
