Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱一觉睡到自然醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love waking up to my own circadian rhythm
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而不是被闹钟叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without the aid of an alarm clock
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我按你说的  一直等到你睡醒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I waited for you to stop sleeping like you asked
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天白天有什么打算  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you got any plans for the day, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll catch ya later
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And leave me alone
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see ya later
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空白的画布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The blank canvas
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蕴含无限的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Infinite possibilities
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.90,0:12:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已知与未知宇宙里所有的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the colors of the known and unknown universe
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都藏在我的调色盘里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hiding on my palette
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,艺术家上前  准备开始创作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The artiste approaches, ready to create
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  要来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986,792)}不要
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see ya later
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.97,0:13:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以在书中的世界探寻幽静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I can find solitude in the printed word
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  要来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(754,348)}第七卷
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see ya later
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.83,0:13:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来玩捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna play hide and seek?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hide first
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧  他跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, where'd he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来他赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he wins
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,失败的味道从来没这么美好过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Defeat has never tasted so sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.90,0:13:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yello?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来玩猜字吊吊乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a game of hangman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.49,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 一人选词一人猜字母，猜错一次\N则画一笔上吊小人，画完或猜对则结束 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要来玩挂电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a game of hang up?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.93,0:13:39.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来没法再悠闲下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:39.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this brings an end to my luxuriating
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要玩鸭鸭寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How 'bout duck, duck hermit crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.46,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自duck duck goose，规则类似丢手绢 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.46,0:13:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopscotch?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说你来做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward says?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.11,0:13:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷培根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steal the bacon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:47.95,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 一队在未被另一队触杀的情况下\N抢走场上的旗子或其他物品 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.95,0:13:48.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沉睡海狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:48.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sleeping sea lions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:48.96,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自sleeping lions\N“狮子”装睡，“猎人”逗醒“狮子” ]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.96,0:13:49.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲨鱼抓小鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:49.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sharks and minnows?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.84,0:13:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击沉潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sink the submarine?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.89,0:13:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kings and queens?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mahjong?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没玩过这游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never played this game before
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.32,0:13:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名字叫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's called
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.84,0:14:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不跟你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will never play with you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远都不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,莫名感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something tells me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥今天不想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Squidward doesn't want to play today
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.39,0:14:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然没法跟真正的章鱼哥玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can't play with the real Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就自己做一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just make one of my own
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个白痴总算开窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think that moron finally gets it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不想再看到他或者听到他在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see or hear him for the
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.92,0:14:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能不能别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, will you make that racket stop
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.72,0:14:37.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:37.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上给我开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You open this door right this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hello Squidward"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Squidward, it's me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.96,0:14:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小小章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mini Squidward"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.65,0:14:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.55,0:15:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又想怎么烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What manner of annoying scheme is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他打声招呼  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just say hello to him, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know how sensitive he is
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now SpongeBob, what the
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.06,0:15:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他比较喜欢别人直呼全名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He prefers to be addressed by his full name
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气很好吧  章鱼哥老兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wondrous weather we're having, eh, Squidward, old pal?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.47,0:15:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝做了替身版的你  也就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob made a replacement you, me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你本尊不想玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So that when you you don't want to play
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝就能跟我这个替身玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob can play with me, you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说你可以顶替我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you'll be filling in for me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪海绵宝宝玩他的笨游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when SpongeBob wants to play one of his stupid games?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.84,0:15:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个词
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three words
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电影名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Movie title
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十二怒水母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,12 angry jellyfish
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.20,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 改自《十二怒汉》 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怎么猜到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106,232)}小小章鱼哥       我
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又猜对了  小小章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right again, squidy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真是个猜谜大师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You little charades master, you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你长得有点不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you look a little different
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最近在健身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you been working out?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  其实这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually Patrick, this is
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你等下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刮了胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shaved your beard
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,476)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁点了蟹  黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who has the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有谁点了蟹黄  堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and who has the Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.15,0:16:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.24,0:16:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为这俩都是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause they're both
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  小小章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, mini Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你永远都是个开心果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are always a ray of sunshine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王又一个美好的工作日了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for another fabulous day of work at the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I am
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love to work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝手上的那个小家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is that little fella with SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  但他好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but isn't he handsome?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  他可真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he is handsome
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉先生  我能为你点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry sir, can I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不喜欢你的态度  小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I don't like your attitude, bub
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这就是蟹堡王所谓的友好服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this what the Krusty Krab calls friendly service?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉先生  我能为你点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry sir, can I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that's more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算有个态度友好的服务生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, a server with a good attitude
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.45,0:17:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这边最好的蟹黄堡来八打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take eight dozen of your finest patties, please
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让那个傻子碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let ol' chowder pants touch 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他多半会玷污了蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He might taint the patties
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  全给你干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine then, go ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,替我干活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do my work for me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要开始喜欢上这位小小章鱼哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm startin' to like this mini Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,替我干活  省得让海绵宝宝来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doing my work, keeping SpongeBob off my back
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻轻松松就能习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could get used to this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  小小章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, mini squid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ok, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.46,0:17:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很乐意帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,always happy to help
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here ya go, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, tiger
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁点了蟹  黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, who had the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有谁点了蟹黄  堡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and who had the Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.92,0:17:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我想的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's my joke
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个新来的小小章鱼哥可真幽默
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This new mini Squidward is such a card
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且服务也周到  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a great waiter, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.71,0:17:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比那个老古板的大号章鱼哥强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So much better
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than that old, lousy, larger-scale Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让那个小家伙过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring that little fella over here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要给他300块的小费
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and let me give him a $300 tip
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我休息完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My break is finished
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  我又来上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我的头足类动物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, me cephalopod
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很遗憾要告诉你这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to tell you this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实也没那么遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, not that sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的客人更喜欢新来的小小章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me customers prefer the new smaller Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.02,0:18:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so do I
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他帮我赚到了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause he's making me some bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你的职务改成勤杂工
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm changing your job to busboy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.72,0:18:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即刻生效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,effective immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静点  看人家怎么干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now pipe down and watch how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥  我爱跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Squidward and I love to dance
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢边吃饭边看跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I for one love to watch people dance while I eat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想要小小章鱼哥跳舞助助兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants mini Squidward to dance for our amusement?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, gosh, OK
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些都是我的舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are all my moves
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是没一点才华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talk about no talent
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.28,0:19:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许章鱼哥得做个缩小手术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe Squidward should get size reduction surgery
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才能跳得好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so he'll dance better
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个小小章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That mini squid
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody dance
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was awful
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他偷了我的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He stole my jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他偷了我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He stole my job
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.97,0:20:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他偷了我的欢呼和掌声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He stole my standing ovation
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个榆木脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You little wooden fiend
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.08,0:20:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再偷我的大好生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop stealing my life
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别咬我新客户的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't gnaw on the head of my new client, please
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不知道你这是在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're doing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饶了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have mercy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen you before
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.27,0:21:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个音乐经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're that music agent
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我最爱的竖笛乐手做经纪的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that represents my favorite clarinet player
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  我是迈罗J芬克尔鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salutations, I'm Milo J Finkerfish
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卷泡唱片的人才管理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talent manager for curly bubbles records
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你是来跟我签合约做唱片的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean you're here to sign me for a record deal?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对此的回答是  免谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The answer to that question is a big n-o
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.29,0:21:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反而这位小家伙才是好得呱呱叫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This little fella on the other hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is woo-hoo, woo-hoo, good
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让他签订百万元合约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're offering him a million-dollar contract
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,636)}合约
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.37,0:21:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附赠一套亮片装
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a sequined suit
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亮片装
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sequined suit
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那才是我应得的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what you're supposed to offer me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与其带走个劣质冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why take a cheap knock-off
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如来找原版得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you can have the original
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要在哪签订
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now where do I sign?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.07,0:21:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你小子想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.49,0:21:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小小章鱼哥  我们的情谊到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, ol' mini Squidward, I guess this is it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.15,0:21:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们曾经猜谜玩得多开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've had some good times playing charades
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.75,0:21:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又像两只轻盈的蝴蝶一样快乐共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and dancing around like two giddy butterflies
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.32,0:22:01.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往日时光真美好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:01.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those were the days
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.65,0:22:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在你也是时候要继续前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's time for you to move on, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迈向更美好的前景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On to greener pastures
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.78,0:22:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  老友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arrivederci, mon frere
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了小子  来轰动全场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right kid, let's go become a sensation
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.42,0:22:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们蛤莱美奖见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we'll see you at the clammy awards
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.75,0:22:18.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  到时多半见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:18.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I guess I won't
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.21,0:22:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  真实大小的章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, actual size Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的梦想破灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My dreams are crushed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.02,0:22:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, hey
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.85,0:22:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码再也不用见到那个小小章鱼哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I won't have to see that mini squid ever again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  我还有更好的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have something even better
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.96,0:22:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另外一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another me
